prompt: Generate a factual, neutral, and descriptive caption of the image. Describe only what is visibly present (furniture, material, color, possible context), without any promotional language, focusing on the main product. Write a single concise noun phrase that captures the essential details without overlooking important and specific features of the furniture (e.g., type, colors, comments on size, shape, material, set, quantity, etc.). Do not describe decorative elements or background details that are not part of the furniture; focus solely on the visible piece or set of furniture.
